data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury living in this stunning estate-style home, nestled in a quiet and serene cul-de-sac in this highly sought-after Summerville community. With a generous .23 acre wooded and private lot, this exquisite single-family residence offers the perfect blend of elegance and comfort, making it the ideal retreat for buyers looking for their dream home.Upon entering, you will be greeted by soaring high ceilings and upgraded hard flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the entire first floor. The open-concept design allows for effortless entertaining, while the gourmet kitchen, complete with high-end features, is perfect for whipping up culinary masterpieces for family and friends. A first-floor bedroom provides a great space for a mother in law suite.Dine in style in the formal dining room boasting coffered ceilings, or enjoy casual meals in the eat-in kitchen. Built-in shelving throughout the home provides ample storage and display opportunities for your cherished belongings.  Retreat to the spacious primary bedroom suite located upstairs, complete with custom closets, a sitting room, and an en-suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms and a generous sized loft offer plenty of space for family and guests. All bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs for ease and privacy.  The outdoor living space is equally impressive, featuring a paver patio in the backyard, perfect for alfresco dining and summer barbecues. With parking for two vehicles and a peaceful setting on a cul-de-sac with no throughway traffic, this is truly a sanctuary that you'll be proud to call home. Don't miss your chance to experience this exquisite estate-style home - schedule a private showing today.
